entries.journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has had her shipment of droid displinary devices stolen by the Valarian. She wants to to steal them back. You need to break into the high security area of the Valarian depot, find EV-9D9's cargo, reprogram a Hauler to move it to a shuttle, kill the piolt and then steal the ship and fly it back to Wayfar.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that you have identified the cargo container that contains EV-9D9's cargo go and reprogram the binary Hauler to take the cargo to the shuttle.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: The cargo has been located and loaded up. The pilot has been eliminated. Go and fly the shuttle back to Wayfar.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Yes. The full cargo is here. Compensation is granted.
